detail.title: v0.5.0 Software Upgrade
detail.description:
### Upgrade to v0.5.0
This governance proposal is for an on-chain upgrade to StaFiHub **v0.5.0** to support receiving liquid staked ATOM shares and then minting corresponding amount of rATOMs for user, which is implemented by using Cosmos LSM.

### Proposal Details
- At block **5868372** StaFiHub will be upgraded to **v0.5.0**
- See changes from **v0.4.3 -> v0.5.0** [here](https://github.com/stafihub/stafihub/compare/v0.4.3...v0.5.0)
- commit hash: **920922cd686a94664f736bd604093a305475d0dc**

### Actionables

If this proposal is successful, all validators and full node operators should upgrade to **v0.5.0** exactly at the upgrade block.
Using cosmovisor is **highly recommended.**

You can find the upgrade countdown [here](https://www.mintscan.io/stafi/blocks/5868372)

And upgrade instruction [here](https://github.com/stafihub/stafihub/tree/main/app/upgrades/v050)

- By voting **YES** you agree to move forward with the network upgrade
- By voting **NO** you disagree to move forward with the network upgrade.

detail.title: Upgrade v0.3.0 - Ledger support
detail.description:
### Upgrade to v0.3.0 - Ledger support
This governance proposal is for an on-chain upgrade to StaFiHub **v0.3.0** to support Ledger.

It also includes version bumps:
- ibc v3.4.0
- cosmos-sdk v0.45.11

### Proposal Details
- At block **2626590** StaFiHub will be upgraded to **v0.3.0**
- See changes from **v0.2.3 -> v0.3.0** [here](https://github.com/stafihub/stafihub/compare/v0.2.3...v0.3.0)
- commit hash: **fd0c05441ce8e6bddd681fa6cb4090697db84c53**

### Actionables

If this proposal is successful, all validators and full node operators should upgrade to **v0.3.0** exactly at the upgrade block.
Using cosmovisor is **highly recommended.**

You can find the upgrade countdown [here](https://www.mintscan.io/stafi/blocks/2626590)
